main event: Two unidentified flying objects were sighted over San Lorenzo Island on 8 July 1965.
interesting points: The first object was sighted at 0905152 and the second at 0907Z., The objects were described as approximately 130 to 150 feet long, cylindrical in shape, and dull metallic in color., They emitted a blowtorch-looking exhaust and a dense black smoke trail., The sighting was made from a military vessel, indicating a military source for the report., The objects flew southeast at a high rate of speed before turning west and disappearing in a puff of smoke.
witness description: Military personnel on a vessel in the area
